title: 01/01/21 – HOUR 1 – Notre Dame Doesn’t Belong in the College Football Playoff!
itunes:title: 01/01/21 – HOUR 1 – Notre Dame Doesn’t Belong in the College Football Playoff!
description:
Rob Parker and T.J. Houshmandzadeh blast Notre Dame for their history of ineptitude in the College Football Playoff and question if the Fighting Irish have the resume to match their #4 overall ranking. Plus, was Dabo Swinney out of line for ranking Ohio State #11 in the Coaches Poll?
